


To start app...



For Windows cmd, use set instead of export:

in terminal...
> set FLASK_APP=forum
> set FLASK_ENV=development
>



to start db if deleted...
in terminal...
> set FLASK_APP=forum
> set FLASK_ENV=development
> flask init-db





- deploying...
https://flask.palletsprojects.com/en/1.1.x/tutorial/deploy/
-




important...
1. Before deployment Secret Key MUST be changed from 'dev' (see https://flask.palletsprojects.com/en/1.1.x/tutorial/factory/)
